WEBVTT

00:06:56.695 --> 00:07:03.198
They were very related in the history
of the country that I was in.

00:07:03.222 --> 00:07:09.790
And it was in the person of Malcolm X
that I learned, for the first time,

00:07:09.814 --> 00:07:14.956
that Islam was deeply ingrained
in the history of this country

00:07:14.980 --> 00:07:19.853
and deeply, deeply relevant
to the struggle of liberation

00:07:19.877 --> 00:07:21.221
in this country.

00:07:21.245 --> 00:07:25.007
And that was when I really transformed
from being a Muslim in America

00:07:25.031 --> 00:07:27.014
to being an American Muslim.

00:07:27.607 --> 00:07:29.760
It was by learning about Malcolm X.

00:07:29.784 --> 00:07:33.658
I went from it being
the religion of my parents,